Package: stick
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, pkexec, coreutils, util-linux
Description: Minimal Linux-only GUI for writing ISO images to USB drives
 Stick is a minimal linux-only GUI for writing ISO images to USB drives.
 .
 It provides a simple GTK3 interface to select an ISO file and a target USB
 drive, and securely flashes the image using system tools like dd and pkexec.